Author: PassionFruitYellow
Text: When my binges were at their worst, I'd eat until I physically couldn't move because of the pain. My stomach would look so strange as the top half of stomach would stick out way further than the bottom half. I wouldn't be able to eat the next day as I'd feel sick and have these sulphuric smelling burps. Luckily now I'm able to stop when I start feeling sick.
